two-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dead_company_two-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dead_company_two-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dead_company_two-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3757422" class="wp-caption-text">死亡与公司在球体。信用：活着的报道</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3757424" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3757424" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3757424" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dead_company_four.jpg" alt="死亡与同伴在球体" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dead_company_four.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dead_company_four-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dead_company_four-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dead_company_four-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dead_company_four-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dead_company_four-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3757424" class="wp-caption-text">死亡与公司在球体。图片来源：飞越芝加哥</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3757425" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3757425" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3757425" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dead_company_three.jpg" alt="死亡与同伴在球体" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dead_company_three.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dead_company_three-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dead_company_three-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/